Package market.world

Class ObjectsAdder

java.lang.Object
market.world.ObjectsAdder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ObjectsAdder extends Object implements Serializable
Class bein able to add new objects to the world in that case it does it randomly. Can write different adder that will be able to do it e.g with only user specified values.
